## Project Description

The Password Manager Encryption project is developed using Python to securely store and manage passwords. This project uses encryption techniques to protect user passwords and improve data security. It provides a simple and user-friendly interface for saving and managing passwords safely.

---

## Features

- Secure password storage
- Password encryption using cryptography
- Generate strong random passwords
- User-friendly GUI using Tkinter
- Save and manage passwords easily
- Secure file handling

---

